Title: Someone's Diary
Text: I just can't stand the dirty looks of the Security Administrator anymore. Gotta remember the combination this time. Now it's only the safest to get it written down! Associations, associations... what should I associate it with? The number of the light strips? That should associate immediately! But that's only one digit, what about the other three? Ah, I should just write it down. Then where should I keep this note? I'll just take a glance when I forget. Where is the safest place to keep it?
